projects.name: Journee
projects.description: Developed Journee, a dynamic web application inspired by Airbnb, using the MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) stack, providing a seamless platform for users to discover, book, and manage travel accommodations. Implemented fully functional login and signup features, allowing users to create accounts and access personalized services. Enabled users to add listings and comments, fostering user engagement and interaction on the platform.

projects.name: TransLingo
projects.description: Developed The Language Translator, a web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, leveraging the Google Translate API to facilitate text translation between multiple languages. Enabled support for over 90 languages, ensuring a diverse range of translation options. Enhanced functionality by integrating the ability for users to upload documents and download translated versions, providing a seamless experience for document translation.

projects.name: Tiger Dev
projects.description: Collaborated on the 'Preservation of the Himalayan Tiger' NFT project, leading UI/UX development and creating captivating digital art highlighting the tigers' significance. Played a pivotal role in the project's success by facilitating effective communication and fostering teamwork among team members.

experiences.description: Led the design of a comprehensive project from start to finish, overseeing all phases from concept to implementation. Implemented front-end development using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React, building responsive and interactive interfaces.

Developed a Text Editor, Translator, and Expense Tracker using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, showcasing proficient web development expertise. Cultivated skills in web development, problem-solving, and teamwork through hands-on project experience.

Focused on identifying and resolving bugs for a movie theater discovery website, ensuring optimal functionality and performance. Utilized React.js to develop and maintain the website, contributing to a smoother and more efficient user interface.
